596
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:02,700
I knew that you wouldn't
had Caleb over to the police.

597
00:34:02,800 --> 00:34:04,700
I knew that
you would protect him.

598
00:34:04,800 --> 00:34:06,300
I would have protected you.

599
