going to get it from me.

608
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:32,500
You know,
I know you believe that.

609
00:34:34,900 --> 00:34:37,400
That's why I've tried
so hard to forgive you.

610
00:34:39,300 --> 00:34:40,700
And who knows?

611
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:44,600
