612
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:03,100
9-1-1.
- What is your emergency?

613
00:35:03,100 --> 00:35:05,700
I need the police.

614
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:14,000
See, I told you
she had cash.

615
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:38,700
Danielle, I don't know
what you're planning,

616
00:35:38,700 --> 00:35:41,600
