658
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:29,000
<i>And I saw</i>
<i>what they brought with them...</i></i>

659
00:40:32,100 --> 00:40:35,900
<i>beautiful dreams</i>
<i>for the future.</i></i>

660
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:40,700
<i>And quiet hopes</i>
<i>for a better life...</i></i>

661
00:40:43,200 --> 00:40:48,400
<i>not just for themselves,</i>
