673
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:32,100
<i>Yes, there will be</i>
<i>unexpected bends in the road,</i></i>

674
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:36,800
<i>shocking surprises</i>
<i>we didn't see coming,</i></i>

675
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:39,800
<i>but that's really the point...</i></i>

676
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:41,300
<i>don't ya think?</i></i>

677
00:41:41,300 --> 00:41:43,100
Orson.
